data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Single story ranch style home on a large .35 acre lot with a shop!! Tons of potential with this property. Hardwood floors under the carpets, forced air heating with A/C, large kitchen and mudroom. Huge fully fenced backyard with large shop, plenty of off street parking, covered back patio and large garden area. Property is zoned General Commercial so could be commercially developed in the future or kept as a single family residence.
